        <updateDate>2021-08-20T13:08:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Better Utilizing Innovative Low-emission Development Strategies Act or the BUILDS Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to establish a grant program to promote reductions in transportation energy use, accelerate the adoption of new and existing energy efficient technologies for transportation applications, and enhance transportation infrastructure.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
